sentences.english: He was buried in the floor of the Mission San Carlos Church.
sentences.chinese: 他在該特派團聖卡洛斯教堂地板埋所有總部。

sentences.english: Daedalus and his son Icarus were prisoners on the island of Crete.
sentences.chinese: 代達羅斯和他的兒子伊卡洛斯是克里特島上的囚犯。

sentences.english: I met Carlos at Sanchez, and we’re still pretty good friends.
sentences.chinese: 在桑切斯我遇到了卡洛斯，我們現在還是要好的朋友。

sentences.english: But they had Carlos Alberto and Roberto Carlos, Jorginho and Cafu.
sentences.chinese: 但是他們有卡洛斯和阿爾伯託，尤爾金霍和卡福。

sentences.english: David: This is Daivd , is Director Carlos here ?
sentences.chinese: 我是大衛，請問卡洛斯主任在嗎？

sentences.english: We need to trade the Icarus for something without Shadow technology.
sentences.chinese: 我們需要把“伊卡洛斯”號更換爲沒有陰影技術的船。

sentences.english: Carlos said he wanted to stay.
I saw my grandchildren, Carlos and Jalea, Ana and Quinito.
sentences.chinese: 我看到我的孫兒們，卡洛斯，傑利，安娜和奎尼託。

sentences.english: Look, Carlos, Mike found out we were spending time together, and he's a little weird about it.
sentences.chinese: 卡洛斯，麥克看見我們昨晚一起了，他有點起疑。

sentences.english: Once the Icarus is repaired you can return to Omicron Sector.
sentences.chinese: 一旦“伊卡洛斯”號修復，你就能返回奧米克戎區。

sentences.english: Skull Leader to Icarus. What's going on, Captain?
sentences.chinese: 骷髏中隊長呼叫“伊卡洛斯”號。發生了什麼，艦長？

sentences.english: Carlos Gardel was born French, but grew up in Argentina.
sentences.chinese: 卡洛斯加德爾原籍法國，但在阿根廷長大。

sentences.english: Sure, Mrs. Tasker. What were you doing with the international terrorist…Carlos the Jackal, taking dictation?
sentences.chinese: 達斯克太太，那你是替國際恐怖份子卡洛斯做速記嗎？

sentences.english: These are the album's liner notes written by maestro Carlos Barbosa Lima.
sentences.chinese: 這是專輯的班輪說明寫的巴博薩大師卡洛斯利馬。

sentences.english: Take the Icarus to the Omicron sector to find the Admiral.
sentences.chinese: 指揮“伊卡洛斯”號去奧米克戎區找到上將。

definition: Logue or Rogge (name)/Jacques Rogge, president of International Olympic Committee (IOC)
